<dl id="n08125o"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n08" href="#n08125o">N08 (VI.B.6)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n08all.htm#n08125o"> 125(o)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> metempsychosis / E = hell</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Their belief in metempsychosis, or the transmigration of souls, the result of their logical rejection of purgatory &hellip;. This earth is a place of punishment, the only hell that exists for the human soul. <small> <a name="CECRA" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#CECRA"><cite title="source">&ldquo;Coemgen&rdquo;, &ldquo;Rosary&rdquo; and &ldquo;Albigenses&rdquo;</cite></a> <cite a>Catholic Encyclopaedia</cite></a> (1911) I, &lsquo;Albigenses&rsquo; 268a</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
